2004;;Going the Distance;;Canadian;;Mark Griffiths;;Christopher Jacot, Joanne Kelly, Shawn Roberts, Ryan Belleville, August Schellenberg;;teen, comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Going_the_Distance_(2004_film);;Nick (Jacot), whose life seemed to be going perfectly, realizes he may lose his girlfriend to a famous music producer (Priestley). He sets out on a roadtrip from the west coast to go to the MuchMusic Video Awards in Toronto, along with two buddies (Tyler and Dime), for the road trip of their lives.